data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to Your Dream Townhome at 10128 Tranquility Way, Cypress Cove Townhomes! Discover the epitome of convenient living in this stunning townhome nestled in the sought-after Cypress Cove Townhomes community. Location, space, and style combine to make this residence an exceptional find. Here's what makes this property a must-see: Step into a spacious kitchen that will inspire your inner chef. Featuring upgraded ceramic tile, upgraded granite counters, a closet pantry, snack bar, and brand-new stainless steel appliances, this kitchen is the heart of the home. NEW ROOF in 2017! This townhome is MOVE-IN READY with NEW floors in the great room, sparkling clean, and NEW paint throughout. It's the perfect canvas for you to make it your own. Added newer water softener in garage. The well-thought-out floorplan places the kitchen, living, and dining areas on the first floor, along with a convenient half bath and a screened porch. Upstairs, you'll find two spacious bedrooms, two full baths, and a laundry room for added convenience. This unit includes an attached 1-car garage with an automatic opener for secure parking and extra storage space. Bring your furry friends along! Cypress Cove Townhomes is a pet-friendly community, ensuring that your four-legged family members feel right at home. Situated in a beautiful development with a sparkling pool, this townhome offers the ideal blend of tranquility and accessibility. Located just 1/2 mile east of the Vet's X-Way at Linebaugh, you'll enjoy easy access to all the Tampa Bay area has to offer.  Citrus Park Mall is just a few minutes north, and downtown Tampa is a quick trip down the Vet's X-Way or various other routes, making it effortless to explore the city's vibrant offerings. Don't miss your chance to make this fantastic townhome your own. With its fantastic location, thoughtful design, and modern amenities, 10128 Tranquility Way is ready to welcome you home. Schedule your showing today and experience the Cypress Cove Townhomes lifestyle for yourself!
